    "# usd_rate.xlsx usd_.xlsx\n",
    "# 3 года\n",
    "dataframe= pd.read_excel('usd_rate.xlsx')\n",
    "dataframe.head()"

      ]

     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "rate = dataframe.curs\n",
    "rate"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 5,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "\n",

      ]

     "output_type": "display_data"

   ],
   "source": [
    "plt.plot(rate, color = 'r')\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 6,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "past = 28 \n",
    "# 4 недели для прогноза из прошлого"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 7,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "с 28 по 738 день\n",
      "всего - 710 дней\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "length = len(rate)\n",
    "count = length - past\n",
    "print(f'с {past} по {length} день\\nвсего - {count} дней')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 8,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "past_days= []\n",
    "current_days= []\n",
    "for day in range(past, length):\n",
    "    past_days.append(list(rate[(day-past):day])) #0:29\n",
    "    current_days.append(rate[day])   #29 rate[day:day+3]"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 9,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "past_columns = []\n",
    "for i in range(past):\n",
    "    past_columns.append(f'past_{i}')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 10,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "X = pd.DataFrame(data = past_days, columns=past_columns)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 11,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "y = pd.Series(current_days, name = 'target')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 12,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# train\n",
    "X_train = X[:-10]\n",
    "y_train = y[:-10]"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 13,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# test\n",
    "X_test = X[-10:]\n",
    "y_test = y[-10:]"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 14,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "from sklearn.metrics import mean_absolute_error"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 15,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "scores= pd.DataFrame()\n",
    "def predictions_plots(model,model_name, features= True):\n",
    "    \n",
    "    model.fit(X_train, y_train)\n",
    "    prediction = model.predict(X_test)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    number = len(scores)\n",
    "    scores.loc[number,'model'] = model_name\n",
    "    scores.loc[number,'score'] = mean_absolute_error(prediction,y_test)\n",
    "    print(scores)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    plt.plot(prediction, label = 'Predicton '+model_name, color='r')\n",
    "    plt.plot(list(y_test),label = 'Real', color='g')\n",
    "    plt.legend()\n",
    "    plt.show()\n",
    "\n",
    "# -----------------\n",
    "    if features:  \n",
    "        try:\n",
    "            imp = pd.Series(list(model.coef_), name='importances') \n",
    "        except AttributeError:\n",
    "            imp = pd.Series(list(model.feature_importances_), name='importances') \n",
    "        cols = pd.Series(past_columns, name='columns')\n",
    "        df = pd.DataFrame(cols)\n",
    "        df['imp'] = imp\n",
    "        print(df)"
   ]
  },

    "from sklearn.model_selection import GridSearchCV"

  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 32,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "regressor = GradientBoostingRegressor(max_depth=5,\n",
    "                                     min_samples_split=3)\n",
    "grid ={\n",
    "    'n_estimators': [50,100,500],\n",
    "    'learning_rate':[0.05,0.1,0.5]\n",
    "}\n",
    "\n",
    "GS = GridSearchCV(regressor, grid, cv = 5, scoring = 'neg_mean_absolute_error')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",

   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {

      "text/plain": [

       "                                                 init=None, learning_rate=0.1,\n",
